    <section id="id1167549255165">
      <title>LEARNING OUTCOME 4: WRITING</title>
      <para id="id6460008">The learner will be able to write different kinds of factual and imaginative texts for a wide range of purposes.</para>
      <section id="id1167558704251">
        <title>Assessment Standard</title>
        <para id="id1167549630838">We know this when the learner:</para>
        <para id="id8172575">4.5 uses developing knowledge of language structure:</para>
        <para id="id8824114">4.5.3 begins to use a wider range of punctuation (e.g. apostrophes).</para>
      </section>
    </section>
    <section id="id1167552172510">
      <title>LEARNING OUTCOME 5: THINKING AND REASONING</title>
      <para id="id1167552172815">The learner will able to use language to think and reason, and access, process and use information for learning.</para>
      <section id="id1167547964311">
        <title>Assessment Standard</title>
        <para id="id6532029">We know this when the learner:</para>
        <para id="id7728606">5.4 transfers information from one mode to another (e.g. chart to text):</para>
        <para id="id1167549781466">5.4.3 uses information from a chart, graph or diagram to write a short text.</para>
      </section>
    </section>
    <section id="id1167559370588">
      <title>LEARNING OUTCOME 6: LANGUAGE STRUCTURE AND USE</title>
      <para id="id1167545299383">The learner will know and be able to use the sounds, words and grammar of the language and interpret texts.</para>
      <section id="id1167559751044">
        <title>Assessment Standard</title>
        <para id="id1167544600672">We know this when the learner:</para>
        <para id="id1167554103100">6.1 understands and uses some question forms, such as ‘Why didn’t ...?’, ‘Have you ever ...?’, ‘Do you think ...?’</para>
        <para id="id1167544829172">6.2 uses the tenses introduced in the Foundation Phase to communicate orally and in writing, e.g.:</para>
        <para id="id1167549684827">6.2.1 simple present tense.</para>
        <para id="id1167545100814"/>
      </section>
    </section>
    <section id="id1167545405398">
      <title>Memorandum</title>
      <para id="id1167556552438">Activity 1</para>
      <para id="id1167559919202">a) Are there four plates on the table?</para>
